citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1330-1400
(1:30-2:00pm) on 02/03/2016. Inspectors called all numbers on file and left a message. Inspector waited 30
minutes in the facility parking lot before leaving the facility with no success at making contact with a facility
representative.

narrative:

ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
